**v0.0.3**

Add lease tracking and enforcement

  - Client leases tracked per-client with 90s timeout (RFC 7530)
  - RENEW operation renews lease timer
  - LOCK implicitly renews lease on success
  - Background goroutine expires stale leases every 30s
  - Expired clients get NFS4ERR_EXPIRED on lock attempts
  - Released locks cleaned up on lease expiry


**v0.0.2**

- Add NFSv4 file locking (LOCK/LOCKT/LOCKU)

Advisory byte-range locking per RFC 7530 Section 9.
Read locks (shared), write locks (exclusive), conflict detection,
grace period for lock reclamation on server restart.


